{"tid":1932183,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"突發!689送手足英國機票，愈多人要愈送得多，聽者有份!","createTime":"2020-03-18T14:43:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-19T11:56:04.000Z","uid":171107,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"9d9069aaa76c84434a9d03d508ea55854068ffd2","tid":1932183,"uid":171107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T14:43:23.000Z","msg":"689: 我送免費倫敦機票<br />\n大批居住在英國的香港人返港避疫，國泰航空公司雖然加大運力至一天五班，但至三月尾的回程航班的所有艙位仍然爆滿，不過，去程的乘客不多。<br />\n既然去程有位，我現在向所有在香港遊行示威時舉英國旗的香港人送免費機票，本月出發，四月回程，名額十個，先到先得。如果反應好，我會擴大送機票計劃給其他人士。<br />\n<br />\n傳送門: <a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1100372063658603&amp;id=100010574583275\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D1100372063658603%26id%3D100010574583275&d=AthmRk%2BBSDjaWf6zT95BzM%2BxtiM4uRDursPVmWLIdz4%3D&h=908a03ff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1100372063658603&amp;id=100010574583275</a>"},{"pid":"6490303733fda9ae848eccce42e9ff0e89d8c38e","tid":1932183,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T14:44:11.000Z","msg":"【媒體懶人堂】三招對抗藍絲文宣戰<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1932182\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1932182</a>"},{"pid":"c2ae5da1f744bdeee616d9e4859945cbae473445","tid":1932183,"uid":171107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T14:46:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a6ae681652c7fdbd980fbf196640d2a3fbb462a8","tid":1932183,"uid":102835,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T14:47:05.000Z","msg":"過氣廢老搏人注意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82581cdcc8ebd29866ede8bcbec6bd043c3dbb23","tid":1932183,"uid":171107,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a6ae681652c7fdbd980fbf196640d2a3fbb462a8","tid":1932183,"uid":102835,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T14:47:05.000Z","msg":"過氣廢